<p>他告诉《每日星报》：“这是我第一次把任何东西扔出去，实际上做了艺术家总是说要做的事情，这不会读任何东西或看任何东西。所以我离开了一切。我感觉真的很棒。”</p><p>他继续说：“我从手机上拿走了Twitter。这是我做过的最好的事情之一。我还没有查找任何东西 - 我就像在幸福的无知中一样。当我们开始演奏时，我会在演出中看到反馈。从历史上看，我们的乐队一直认为我们在门票销售上的成功比其他任何东西都不是其他评论。”</p><p>芒福德（Mumford）继续承认，在现场表演时，民间摇滚歌手是“瘾君子”。他补充说：“让我们看看观众的样子以及人们对我们音乐的生活感，因为那是我们唯一的真实方式。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="NME遇到Mumford＆Sons的Marcus和Winston来谈论折衷的新专辑“ Delta”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/h51VzMkXJB8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>今年晚些时候，Mumford＆Sons将踏上大规模的英国和欧洲竞技场之旅，该巡回赛将于11月开始，并在12月初结束。您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mumford-sons-add-new-dates-to-2025-uk-arena-tour-after-all-shows-sell-out-within-two-hours-3848819" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处查看日期的完整列表</a>，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fmumford-sons-tickets%2Fartist%2F1388154" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买门票。</p><p>乐队已经实施了1英镑的捐款来为英国售出的每张票证的<a href="https://livemusic.biz/live-trust" target="_blank" rel="noopener">现场信托</a>捐款，这笔钱用于Live的新资助计划，为从事现场音乐工作的人们提供了财务支持。他们还与Plus1合作，因此每张售出的门票中的1英镑都会流向<a href="https://www.warchild.org.uk/donate-gazaemergencyappeal-2024-paidsearch?gad_source=1&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQjw4cS-BhDGARIsABg4_J1nW0jCN3ejBncIbAC81-BL9iHgISaMEuHKa3QDNxlOVlBxDwhx2pMaAmOVEALw_wcB" target="_blank" rel="noopener">战争孩子</a>。</p><p>他们还将在今年夏天晚些时候踏上32天的北美竞技场和圆形剧场之旅。您可以访问<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fmumford-sons-tickets%2Fartist%2F1388154" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。巡回演出支持他们的新专辑“ Rushmere”。</p><p>在其他新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jimmy-fallon">吉米·法伦（Jimmy Fallon）</a>最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-jimmy-fallon-give-mumford-sons-hilariously-long-intro-on-tonight-show-after-snl-50-concert-snub-3849647">在<em>今晚</em>的玛库斯·芒</a>福德（Marcus Mumford）在今年早些时候在<em>《星期六夜现场》（Saturday Night Live）成立</em>50周年音乐会上为乐队的痛苦简短介绍而在今晚秀上的蒙福德和儿子们进行了漫长的简介。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mumford-sons-share-powerful-advice-from-neil-young-youve-got-it-all-wrong-man-3850129">Mumford＆Sons Post向Neil Young分享了强有力的建议：“您错了，男人”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
黑蜂蜜在虚无的新单曲“ Psycho”上“下降兔子洞” https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-honey-go-down-the-rabbit-hole-on-nihilistic-new-single-psycho-3850116?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=black-honey-go-down-the-rabbit-hole-on-nihilistic-new-single-psychoLaura Molloy Fri, 28 Mar 2025 14:32:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music NewsRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3850116 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们还宣布了三场英国演出将于4月开始</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首先出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-honey-go-down-the-rabbit-hole-on-nihilistic-new-single-psycho-3850116">Nihilistic New Single“ Psycho”上的黑蜂蜜“ Down the Rabbit Hole”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Black-Honey.-CREDIT_-Press-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-honey">黑蜂蜜</a>分享了他们的虚无的新单曲“ Psycho”。在下面查看。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/black-honey-live-in-kingston-pryzm-review-2978538">金斯敦的黑蜂蜜现场：布莱顿人是乐队释放</a></strong></li></ul><p>自从他们在2023年专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-honey-announce-third-album-a-fistful-of-peaches-with-new-single-heavy-3345721">A Fistful of Peaches</a> ”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-honey-share-angsty-new-single-lemonade-announce-2024-tour-3521410">后续单曲“ Lemonade”</a>发行后，这标志着乐队的第一个新材料。</p><p>将黑暗的流行元素与令人毛骨悚然的岩石融合在一起，曲目使它们探究了现代生活的黑暗现实。</p><p>歌手B. Phillips解释说：“ Psycho是一种荒谬的，在兔子洞中的感觉，在感觉真的超现实的事物中成为偷窥狂。” “这是关于想知道这一生是否是&#39;电影&#39;，也许是写得不好。有点虚无主义，并以更大的看法逃脱了平凡的，精神病和生存。”</p><p>它与布拉夫·弗罗斯特（Harv Frost）执导的<em>发条橙色</em>的视频伴随着，随着菲利普斯（Phillips）被困在反乌托邦的设施中时，她的乐队成员将她绑在椅子上，并强迫她的捏造经历，直到她变得麻木。在下面查看。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="黑蜂蜜 - 心理" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/M_uYiJGD-Cc?list=PL4tDzwvVvC5jA9XxUbctauA4H4BCeiAoj&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Alongside the new single, Black Honey have announced a string of UK shows for April to mark their return to the stage. They&#39;ll kick things off on April 15 at Manchester&#39;s Night &amp; Day, before heading to Brighton&#39;s Pattern and London&#39;s Omeara.</p><p> Tickets are available via a private ballot system. You can sign up <a href="https://blackhoney.os.fan/april-2025-shows-registration?fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAaZ39Mv_Txog1-1e5MYYZWIvq04MNXiSN_SxeygBdirw21YwwNEAiFCvjr8_aem_8emAkIPfa9XuyXYVFYvnUg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> for a chance to access them when they go on sale.</p><p> It&#39;s not yet clear if the single comes from an upcoming album, but the band shared on Instagram that they&#39;ll be playing “some new stuff” at the upcoming live shows.</p><h3> <strong>Black Honey&#39;s 2025 shows are:</strong></h3><p><strong>四月</strong><br /><strong>15 – Manchester, Night &amp; Day</strong><br /> <strong>16 – Brighton, Pattern</strong><br /> <strong>17 – London, Omeara</strong> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Glastonbury 2017: Backstage with Black Honey" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/glzIs9mqtHE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <em>NME</em> caught them live in Kingston in 2021 and gave the show a <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/black-honey-live-in-kingston-pryzm-review-2978538">glowing four-star review</a> , describing the gig as “loud and raucous, and despite all the safety precautions, it feels dangerous.”</p><p> It went on to say: “Black Honey look like a band unleashed. Philips fights back tears before the ferocious close of &#39;Run For Cover&#39; and, true to form, her microphone breaks in the middle of the song. Clearly expecting the worst, she doesn&#39;t skip a beat and finds a spare. Turns out you really can&#39;t keep a great band down.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-honey-go-down-the-rabbit-hole-on-nihilistic-new-single-psycho-3850116">Black Honey go “down the rabbit hole” on nihilistic new single &#39;Psycho&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
