hite-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rachel-Zegler-Snow-White-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rachel-Zegler-Snow-White-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rachel-Zegler-Snow-White-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Rachel-Zegler-Snow-White-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> The troubles of <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">Disney&#39;s</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/snow-white"><em>Snow White</em></a> remake continued, as website <em>IMDb</em> (Internet Movie Database) has listed it as one of the worst movies ever, according to user ratings.</p><p>在网站上，允许注册用户在10个中的单个电影中得分，得分会导致加权平均值。 Currently, <em>Snow White</em> sits at a lowly 1.6 out of ten rating.</p><p> According to <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt6208148/ratings/?ref_=tt_ov_rat" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the breakdown</a> , 90 per cent of those voting, over 180,000, gave it a one out of 10 rating. A little over 5,000 users (or 2.5 per cent) gave it the full 10 out of 10. The weighted score based on just under 200,000 votes is 1.6, placing it lower than famous flops such as 2000&#39;s <em>Battlefield Earth</em> (two out of 10) and 2019 musical <em>Cats</em> (2.8).</p><p> The figures make grim reading for the film, with the release being overshadowed by poor reviews and controversy surrounding star <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-zegler">Rachel Zegler</a> . Several changes were made to the 1937 original film, giving Snow White a more political focus, changing the background of the seven dwarves, and altering aspects of the plot. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Disney’s Snow White |官方预告片| In Theaters March 21" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iV46TJKL8cU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p> The film currently sits at a “rotten” 42 per cent score on review aggregator <a href="https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/disneys_snow_white" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Rotten Tomatoes</em></a> , and debuted to $42.2million at the US box office last weekend, well below expectations and a disaster considering the film&#39;s estimated $240–270million budget.</p><p> That opening was lower than 2019&#39;s <em>Dumbo</em> , which was a box office bomb and ultimately lost Disney money given the reported cost to make and market the project. The studio will be hoping that this is merely a blip in the momentum of its live-action remakes, with <em>Lilo &amp; Stitch</em> released in May and <em>Moana</em> coming to cinemas in 2026.</p><p> Recently, a report said that Disney <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/rachel-zegler-had-social-media-guru-paid-for-by-disney-after-fuck-trump-posts-3849428">hired a “social media guru”</a> to vet Zegler&#39;s posts after making derogatory remarks about President Donald Trump. Meanwhile her co-star <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gal-gadot">Gal Gadot</a> , who plays the evil queen in the film, shrugged off backlash she has received for pro-Israel comments, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/gal-gadot-shrugs-off-backlash-pro-israel-comments-my-conscience-is-clean-3847482">remarking: ”My conscience is clean”.</a></p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/snow-white-remake-is-one-of-the-worst-movies-of-all-time-according-to-imdb-users-3850107">&#39;Snow White&#39; remake is one of the worst movies of all time, according to IMDB users</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
