 I love.” Check out her cover below. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Dua Lipa - Never Tear Us Apart [INXS Cover] (Live at Radical Optimism Tour in Sydney) 26/3/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OL4XrvTopF0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> While on tour down under, Lipa has made headlines with an eclectic mixture of covers, including <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-covers-aussie-legend-kylie-minogues-cant-get-you-out-of-my-head-in-melbourne-3847894">Kylie Minogue&#39;s &#39;Can&#39;t Get You Out Of My Head&#39;</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dua-lipa-cover-natalie-imbruglias-torn-during-second-melbourne-concert-3847685">Natalie Imbruglia&#39;s &#39;Torn&#39;</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dua-lipa-cover-ac-dcs-highway-to-hell-in-melbourne-3847044">AC/DC&#39;s &#39;Highway To Hell&#39;</a> .</p><p> She also brought out <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vance-joy">Vance Joy</a> for <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dua-lipa-cover-riptide-with-vance-joy-at-melbourne-show-3848777">a cover of &#39;Riptide&#39;</a> at her final Melbourne show, and treated the audience to <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-troye-sivan-join-dua-lipa-for-rush-duet-in-melbourne-3848471">a surprise appearance</a> from <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/troye-sivan">Troye Sivan</a> .</p><p> After wrapping up in Australia, Lipa is heading <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-adds-uk-europe-australia-and-north-america-dates-to-2025-radical-optimism-tour-3793188">to the UK for even more live shows this summer</a> , kicking off the run with <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-unveils-details-of-huge-wembley-show-in-2025-3771131">two huge concerts at London&#39;s Wembley Stadium (June 20, 21)</a> followed by <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-adds-second-liverpol-show-to-2025-radical-optimism-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-buy-tickets-3795605">two dates at Anfield Stadium in Liverpool on June 24 and 25</a> .</p><p> Before then, she&#39;ll be touring across Europe performing in Paris, Belgium, Milan, Amsterdam and more. Visit <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fdua-lipa-tickets%2Fartist%2F2179476" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> for Europe tickets and <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fdua-lipa-tickets%2Fartist%2F2179476" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> for UK tickets. The dates come following her huge <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/dua-lipa-live-at-glastonbury-2024-review-setlist-photos-3770003">headline slot at Glastonbury 2024</a> . </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Dua Lipa I 90-second Interview" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xVoT6EZHOPE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> In other news, earlier today (March 28) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-and-troye-sivan-team-up-on-physical-remix-for-fifth-anniversary-of-future-nostalgia-3849949">Lipa shared a new version of her 2020 hit song &#39;Physical&#39;, including a new feature from Sivan</a> .</p><p> It comes as part of a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-announces-special-fifth-anniversary-vinyl-re-release-of-future-nostalgia-3837491">special re-release of &#39;Future Nostalgia&#39; in celebration of its fifth anniversary</a> .乙烯基套件今天已经发行，几乎是专辑首次播放后的五年。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/n